# News Ingestion

## Source Processing

Supported:

- RSS
- Atom

Primary library:

- feedparser

---

## Content Extraction

Primary library:

- BeautifulSoup

Extraction goals:

- remove navigation
- remove scripts
- remove ads
- remove styles

Store only readable text.

---

## Chunking

Chunk size:

- 500 characters

Overlap:

- 100 characters

Configurable through settings.

---

## Embeddings

Library:

- Sentence Transformers

Default model:

```text
all-MiniLM-L6-v2
```

Embedding generation must be isolated behind an interface.

---

## Duplicate Prevention

Before storing chunk:

1. Check existing text hash
2. Skip duplicates

---

## Failures

Failures for one source must not stop processing of other sources.

Processing must continue.

All failures must be logged.